[{'text': '[Intro]', 'start': 1.77, 'duration': 10.13}, {'text': '[sad noises]', 'start': 11.9, 'duration': 8.9}, {'text': 'Jessi: Oh hey, guys! We were just practicing
our sad faces.', 'start': 20.8, 'duration': 2.5}, {'text': 'Ooo, good one, Squeaks!', 'start': 23.32, 'duration': 2.37}, {'text': 'Chances are you cant look any more miserable
than this deep-sea creature: Meet the blobfish!', 'start': 25.69, 'duration': 5.52}, {'text': 'Its got a pretty good reason to look so
bummed. Its been called the worlds ugliest', 'start': 31.21, 'duration': 5.119}, {'text': 'animal.', 'start': 36.329, 'duration': 1.051}, {'text': 'Which really isnt a nice thing to say.', 'start': 37.38, 'duration': 1.82}, {'text': 'I mean, it might not be as cute as a panda
or a kitten, but the blobfishs funny-looking', 'start': 39.2, 'duration': 4.48}, {'text': 'body actually helps it to survive in its harsh
underwater environment.', 'start': 43.68, 'duration': 4.45}, {'text': 'The blobfish lives in the ocean off the coast
of Australia. And it lives really, really', 'start': 48.13, 'duration': 4.72}, {'text': 'deep.', 'start': 52.85, 'duration': 0.389}, {'text': 'How deep? Almost at the sea floor -- thats
nearly 10 times deeper than where most ocean', 'start': 53.239, 'duration': 5.59}, {'text': 'animals live.', 'start': 58.829, 'duration': 1.431}, {'text': 'Not many animals could survive where the blobfish
lives.', 'start': 60.26, 'duration': 3.299}, {'text': 'Down there, its pitch-black because sunlight
cant even reach that far; the temperature', 'start': 63.559, 'duration': 4.52}, {'text': 'is just a few degrees above freezing; and
the pressure is extremely high.', 'start': 68.079, 'duration': 5.271}, {'text': 'So whats this pressure were talking
about? Well, if youre at the bottom of', 'start': 73.35, 'duration': 3.28}, {'text': 'the ocean, the weight of alllll the water
on top of you presses down really hard. And', 'start': 76.63, 'duration': 5.07}, {'text': 'it squeezes you -- like a really, really tight
bear hug!', 'start': 81.7, 'duration': 3.629}, {'text': 'So how does the blobfish survive with all
this intense pressure? Well, thats where', 'start': 85.329, 'duration': 4.46}, {'text': 'its ugliness is actually a plus!', 'start': 89.789, 'duration': 2.67}, {'text': 'The blobfish has a gooey, jelly-like body
that can handle the squeezing from all of', 'start': 92.459, 'duration': 4.48}, {'text': 'that underwater pressure.', 'start': 96.939, 'duration': 1.38}, {'text': 'In fact, it has almost no muscle, and very
few bones. Its almost pure squish!', 'start': 98.319, 'duration': 5.72}, {'text': 'But its still able to do things like move
and eat, because its blobbiness makes it buoyant.', 'start': 104.039, 'duration': 5.15}, {'text': 'And this means it can just float comfortably
right above the ocean floor without having', 'start': 109.189, 'duration': 4.56}, {'text': 'to use too much energy to swim.', 'start': 113.749, 'duration': 2.18}, {'text': 'And it mostly just swallows food that happens
to float on by.', 'start': 115.929, 'duration': 3.79}, {'text': 'Which I have to admit would be pretty neat.
Could you imagine cheeseburgers just floating', 'start': 119.719, 'duration': 4.68}, {'text': 'into your mouth?!', 'start': 124.399, 'duration': 1.121}, {'text': 'So the blobfish is blobby for a lot of good
reasons. And to its underwater friends, it', 'start': 125.52, 'duration': 5.79}, {'text': 'probably doesnt look so ugly at all.', 'start': 131.31, 'duration': 1.89}, {'text': 'Scientists actually think that -- when its
at home on the ocean floor -- the blobfish', 'start': 133.2, 'duration': 4.39}, {'text': 'probably looks more like the other fish that
we know. Thats because the pressure at', 'start': 137.59, 'duration': 4.12}, {'text': 'the bottom of the ocean squeezes its body
into that shape.', 'start': 141.71, 'duration': 3.68}, {'text': "But most of the blobfish that we've seen have
been caught by fishing nets, and brought up", 'start': 145.39, 'duration': 4.48}, {'text': 'out of the ocean.', 'start': 149.87, 'duration': 1.3}, {'text': 'And when a blobfish is taken away from the
pressure that gives its body that shape, well,', 'start': 151.17, 'duration': 4.2}, {'text': 'it looks blobbier than usual.', 'start': 155.37, 'duration': 2.47}, {'text': 'So is the blobfish really ugly? Well, maybe
to some people.', 'start': 157.84, 'duration': 3.96}, {'text': 'Is it awesome? Definitely.', 'start': 161.8, 'duration': 1.99}, {'text': 'Thanks for learning about the blobfish with
